title: Good Movie to Watch
review: Solid performances and brilliant production design. It has many moments which you will remember of rest of the life. Tom Malloy is a start performer. All said and done, it's definitely a good movie to watch!

title: All Stars
review: I must say Trauma Therapy gains all the marks in keeping us thrilled till the end. Big credits to the writers and directional team. Great job done!

title: An Extra-Ordinary Movie
review: This movie really hit me hard, I have explored so many suspense movies and this one is also good. With a shoe string budget, they have made an extra-ordinary movie. Ultimate experience!
